This paper deals with building an automatic system to recognize affect of human facial expression in real-world conditions, which is a problem in the field of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.MM). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning techniques, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper focuses on the application of this system in human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
